  <RulesElement name="Bed of Leaves (heroic tier)" type="Magic Item" internal-id="ID_EOF_MAGIC_ITEM_11005_01" source="Buck-A-Batch Wondrous Items 2" revision-date="6/26/2011 10:26 PM">
    <Flavor> This magic bedroll, favored by the fey, resembles a pile of leaves when in use, a flurry of leaves when disturbed. </Flavor>
    <specific name="Level"> 3 </specific>
    <specific name="Gold"> 680 </specific>
    <specific name="Magic Item Type"> Wondrous Item </specific>
    <specific name="Tier" />
    <specific name="_Item_Set_ID" />
    <specific name="Armor" />
    <specific name="Weapon" />
    <specific name="Item Slot" />
    <specific name="Requirement" />
    <specific name="Critical" />
    <specific name="Property"> While sleeping in this bedroll in a forest setting you gain total concealment. Creatures attempting to find you suffer a -5 penalty to their perception checks. </specific>
    <specific name="Special" />
    <specific name="Power"> Power (Daily): Immediate Reaction. This ability triggers when a creature makes a successful attack against you while you are sleeping in the bedroll. The attack misses. You immediately wake and teleport up to 5 squares away. Make an attack: Attacking creature and enemy creatures in squares adjacent to the bedroll; +5 vs. Will; hit: creatures are stunned (save ends). </specific>
    <specific name="_Rarity"> Common </specific>
    <specific name="Granted Powers" />
  </RulesElement>
  <RulesElement name="Bug in a Bottle (heroic tier)" type="Magic Item" internal-id="ID_EOF_MAGIC_ITEM_11005_02" source="Buck-A-Batch Wondrous Items 2" revision-date="6/26/2011 10:39 PM">
    <Flavor> A small glass bottle holds a large and nasty looking beetle. It seems impervious to harm. </Flavor>
    <specific name="Level"> 5 </specific>
    <specific name="Gold"> 1000 </specific>
    <specific name="Magic Item Type"> Wondrous Item </specific>
    <specific name="Tier" />
    <specific name="_Item_Set_ID" />
    <specific name="Armor" />
    <specific name="Weapon" />
    <specific name="Item Slot" />
    <specific name="Requirement" />
    <specific name="Critical" />
    <specific name="Property" />
    <specific name="Special" />
    <specific name="Power"> Power (Encounter): Immediate Interrupt. Use this ability when you would be dealt ongoing damage. The ongoing damage effect is transferred to the beetle. The beetle will, burn, freeze, spark, etc. depending upon the damage type, however it will not die. The ongoing damage effect ends as normal or at the end of the encounter. </specific>
    <specific name="_Rarity"> Common </specific>
    <specific name="Granted Powers" />
  </RulesElement>
  <RulesElement name="Burglar's Bane Mask (heroic tier)" type="Magic Item" internal-id="ID_EOF_MAGIC_ITEM_11005_03" source="Buck-A-Batch Wondrous Items 2" revision-date="6/26/2011 10:42 PM">
    <Flavor> A tribal mask of an angry beast; part wall hanging, part watchdog. </Flavor>
    <specific name="Level"> 2 </specific>
    <specific name="Gold"> 520 </specific>
    <specific name="Magic Item Type"> Wondrous Item </specific>
    <specific name="Tier" />
    <specific name="_Item_Set_ID" />
    <specific name="Armor" />
    <specific name="Weapon" />
    <specific name="Item Slot" />
    <specific name="Requirement" />
    <specific name="Critical" />
    <specific name="Property"> When placed on the wall of a room the mask makes note of all occupants within 30 feet of it. If a creature it hasn't noted as an occupant passes with 10 feet of it, it will emit a loud roar, waking and/or alerting anyone within earshot. It will continue to emit its roars every few seconds until the intruder moves more than 30 feet away from it or the owner wills it to stop. </specific>
    <specific name="Special" />
    <specific name="Power" />
    <specific name="_Rarity"> Common </specific>
    <specific name="Granted Powers" />
  </RulesElement>
  <RulesElement name="Cacklefiend Bag (heroic tier)" type="Magic Item" internal-id="ID_EOF_MAGIC_ITEM_11005_04" source="Buck-A-Batch Wondrous Items 2" revision-date="6/26/2011 10:46 PM">
    <Flavor> A patchwork bag of stitched together hyena hides. It retains some remnants of its previous wearers. </Flavor>
