    <specific name="_Item_Set_ID" />
    <specific name="Armor" />
    <specific name="Weapon" />
    <specific name="Item Slot" />
    <specific name="Requirement" />
    <specific name="Critical" />
    <specific name="Property"> The first time each day that this bag is touched by someone other than its owner the power listed below triggers. </specific>
    <specific name="Special" />
    <specific name="Power"> Power (Encounter * Fear): Minor Action. Close burst 3; targets enemies; deafened creatures are immune; +8 vs Will; the target takes a -2 penalty to attack rolls until the end of your next turn. </specific>
    <specific name="_Rarity"> Common </specific>
