  </RulesElement>
  <RulesElement name="Crown of Doors (heroic tier)" type="Magic Item" internal-id="ID_EOF_MAGIC_ITEM_11005_05" source="Buck-A-Batch Wondrous Items 2" revision-date="6/26/2011 10:50 PM">
    <Flavor> Five tiny floating doors circle your head like a crown. You've just been crowned king of somewhere else. </Flavor>
    <specific name="Level"> 10 </specific>
    <specific name="Gold"> 5000 </specific>
    <specific name="Magic Item Type"> Wondrous Item </specific>
    <specific name="Tier" />
    <specific name="_Item_Set_ID" />
    <specific name="Armor" />
    <specific name="Weapon" />
    <specific name="Item Slot" />
    <specific name="Requirement" />
    <specific name="Critical" />
    <specific name="Property"> You gain a +2 bonus to door related perception checks; listen at a door, detect a trapped door, etc. You gain a +2 bonus to strength checks when breaking down a door or opening a portcullis. </specific>
    <specific name="Special" />
    <specific name="Power"> Power (Daily): Standard Action. When you touch a locked door, or locked door-like obstacle, such as a gate or portcullis, make a Thievery check with a +20 bonus against the DC required to open the lock. 
Power (Daily * Teleportation): Move Action. You gain the ability to use dimension door as the Wizard's 6 level utility power. </specific>
    <specific name="_Rarity"> Common </specific>
    <specific name="Granted Powers" />
  </RulesElement>
