  <RulesElement name="Fire-Burst Shatterstone (heroic tier)" type="Magic Item" internal-id="ID_EOF_MAGIC_ITEM_11005_08" source="Buck-A-Batch Wondrous Items 2" revision-date="6/26/2011 11:02 PM">
    <Flavor> This glowing stone is hot to the touch. When struck with force it shatters, releasing an energy attack. </Flavor>
    <specific name="Level"> 1 </specific>
    <specific name="Gold"> 360 </specific>
    <specific name="Magic Item Type"> Wondrous Item </specific>
    <specific name="Tier" />
    <specific name="_Item_Set_ID" />
    <specific name="Armor" />
    <specific name="Weapon" />
    <specific name="Item Slot" />
    <specific name="Requirement" />
    <specific name="Critical" />
    <specific name="Property"> A skilled blacksmith can attach a fire-burst shatterstone to any blunt non-magic weapon, such as a staff, club, mace or hammer. Once attached the weapon gains a +1 bonus to hit and deals 1 point fire damage in addition to its normal damage. </specific>
    <specific name="Special" />
    <specific name="Power"> Power (Consumable * Fire): Free Action. You may trigger this ability when you score a critical hit on a creature with the weapon that the shatterstone is attached to. You deal an additional 5 fire damage to the target and any enemy creatures in spaces adjacent to the target. All creatures damaged in this way take ongoing 5 fire damage (save ends). After this that shatterstone is destroyed. </specific>
    <specific name="_Rarity"> Common </specific>
    <specific name="Granted Powers" />
  </RulesElement>
