  <RulesElement name="Memory Egg (heroic tier)" type="Magic Item" internal-id="ID_EOF_MAGIC_ITEM_11005_19" source="Buck-A-Batch Wondrous Items 2" revision-date="6/26/2011 11:44 PM">
    <Flavor> A metal egg with a brass button on one side. It's hollow and bears lenses set over holes in its top and bottom. </Flavor>
    <specific name="Level"> 5 </specific>
    <specific name="Gold"> 1000 </specific>
    <specific name="Magic Item Type"> Wondrous Item </specific>
    <specific name="Tier" />
    <specific name="_Item_Set_ID" />
    <specific name="Armor" />
    <specific name="Weapon" />
    <specific name="Item Slot" />
    <specific name="Requirement" />
    <specific name="Critical" />
    <specific name="Property"> Pressing the brass button on the side of the egg while peering through it at an object will cause the image of that object to become trapped in the egg. Shaking the egg once will cause the image to become stored allowing additional images to be captured. Shaking the egg a number of times allows the owner to cycle through stored images which can be viewed by looking into the egg. Holding down the button and shaking the egg while it's displaying an image will cause that image to be deleted. The egg can hold a total of 12 images. The act of trapping an image is accompanied by a flash of light. </specific>
    <specific name="Special" />
    <specific name="Power"> Power (Encounter): Minor Action. Close burst 3; targets enemies; blind creatures are immune; +8 vs Will; Hit: the target becomes dazed (save ends). </specific>
    <specific name="_Rarity"> Common </specific>
    <specific name="Granted Powers" />
  </RulesElement>
  <RulesElement name="Merchant's Coin Purse (heroic tier)" type="Magic Item" internal-id="ID_EOF_MAGIC_ITEM_11005_20" source="Buck-A-Batch Wondrous Items 2" revision-date="6/26/2011 11:49 PM">
    <Flavor> A simple yet effective enchantment conceals the true amount of coins in your possession. </Flavor>
    <specific name="Level"> 4 </specific>
    <specific name="Gold"> 840 </specific>
    <specific name="Magic Item Type"> Wondrous Item </specific>
    <specific name="Tier" />
    <specific name="_Item_Set_ID" />
    <specific name="Armor" />
    <specific name="Weapon" />
    <specific name="Item Slot" />
    <specific name="Requirement" />
    <specific name="Critical" />
    <specific name="Property"> Twisting the clasp on this coin purse one way will cause it to inflate and activate an audible illusion, making it seem to contain far more coins than it actually does. Twisting the clasp the other way will shrink the bag and activate a spell that deadens the noise generated by any coins within while moving. </specific>
    <specific name="Special" />
    <specific name="Power" />
    <specific name="_Rarity"> Common </specific>
