  <RulesElement name="Moocher's Mug (heroic tier)" type="Magic Item" internal-id="ID_EOF_MAGIC_ITEM_11005_21" source="Buck-A-Batch Wondrous Items 2" revision-date="6/26/2011 11:56 PM">
    <Flavor> This mug will get you a portion of your neighbor's ale on the sly. It will also get you kicked out of most taverns. </Flavor>
